Package: ggsemplot
Title: Publication-Quality SEM Path Diagrams with 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("ggsemplot", "authors", email = "ggsemplot@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create beautiful, publication-ready structural equation model (SEM)
    path diagrams using 'ggplot2'. Provides a rich theme system with multiple
    preset styles (classic, modern, APA, minimal, Nature, dark, colorful),
    intelligent automatic layouts, and a declarative API. Extracts model
    information from 'lavaan' and related packages, then renders nodes, edges,
    and labels as native 'ggplot2' layers for full customizability.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ggsemplot/ggsemplot
BugReports: https://github.com/ggsemplot/ggsemplot/issues
